00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:30,628
There's a tricky step.
I keep meaning to fix it.

282
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:34,919
What a beautiful bed.

283
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:37,958
-Could I use your bathroom?
-Would you use the one downstairs?

284
00:15:38,040 --> 00:15:40,713
All my personal things
are still in this one.

285
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:42,791
Oh. Sure.

286
00:15:44,760 --> 00:15:48,435
Happiest moments of my life
since we left Paraguay...

287
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:51,114
have been spent
right here in this room.

288
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:53,031
You lived in Paraguay?

289
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:55,509
Ten wonderful years.

290
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:58,319
Carlos is from Asuncion.

291
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:02,557
Or at least he...
[Weeping]

292
