I'm awfully sorry.

293
00:16:11,920 --> 00:16:13,797
About what?

294
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:17,071
I don't know actually.

295
00:16:17,160 --> 00:16:19,515
Do you wanna
buy the bed?

296
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:22,239
l-I think so.

297
00:16:22,320 --> 00:16:27,314
You know, you think
you know somebody...

298
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:29,516
after 25 years...

299
