00:23:09,080 --> 00:23:11,913
<i>[Hammering Continues]</i>

413
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:23,311
How's it going?

414
00:23:23,400 --> 00:23:27,029
Fine. What's that
on your face?

415
00:23:27,120 --> 00:23:29,509
The ceiling.

416
00:23:29,600 --> 00:23:31,636
Seems to be coming down
in the bedroom.

417
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:34,553
Oh. Well, I'll get to that later.
I only got two hands.

418
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:36,870
-Okay. [Chuckling]
-<i>Okay.</i>

419
00:23:39,360 --> 00:23:42,158
[Groaning]

420
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:05,316
[Squeaking, Clanging]

421
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:07,436
<i>[Clanging Continues]</i>

422
00:24:19,680 --> 00:24:21,955
What the hell
was that?

423
00:24:22,040 --> 00:24:24,235
All I did was
turn on the water.

424
00:24:24,320 --> 00:24:27,915
-That's all?
-<i>[Squeaking, Banging]</i>

425
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:29,831
That doesn't sound good.

426
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:33,117
No.
You should see the...

427
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:35,475
I guess it's the water.

428
00:24:35,560 --> 00:24:37,630
-I don't know. It's revolting.
-<i>Okay.</i>

429
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:40,314
So the plumbing's
not perfect.

430
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:42,789
We'll get it fixed.
