01:05:03,080 --> 01:05:04,911
-## [Continues]
-You'd better let me off here.

1086
01:05:05,000 --> 01:05:07,798
-I don't think you can
make it up the driveway.
-They testin' missiles here?

1087
01:05:07,880 --> 01:05:10,678
That's right, buddy, we are,
and it's very hush-hush. Top secret.

1088
01:05:10,760 --> 01:05:13,877
So forget you were up here
and forget you saw any of this.

1089
01:05:13,960 --> 01:05:17,430
-And forget about a tip.
-[Man, Children On Tape]
# I am a pizza #

1090
01:05:17,520 --> 01:05:20,990
-# Ready to munch #
-Ah, home, crap home.

1091
01:05:21,080 --> 01:05:23,548
-<i># I am a pizza #</i>
-<i># I am a pi... ##</i>

1092
01:05:23,640 --> 01:05:27,428
I still can't get used to the idea of
having hot water whenever we want it.

1093
01:05:27,520 --> 01:05:29,988
Yeah.
Yeah.

1094
01:05:30,080 --> 01:05:32,878
-So, what'd you do last night?
-<i>Oh, nothing much.</i>

1095
01:05:32,960 --> 01:05:34,791
Where'd you eat?

1096
01:05:34,880 --> 01:05:36,711
What?

1097
01:05:36,800 --> 01:05:38,631
<i>Last night.</i>
<i>Where did you eat?</i>

1098
01:05:38,720 --> 01:05:41,234
Oh.
The Four Seasons.

1099
01:05:41,320 --> 01:05:43,595
Well, I'm glad it wasn't
anything special.

1100
01:05:43,680 --> 01:05:45,511
Actually,
it was a little special.

1101
01:05:45,600 --> 01:05:47,909
We had just done probably
the finest performance...

1102
01:05:48,000 --> 01:05:49,991
of Haydn's
Surprise Symphony ever.

1103
01:05:50,080 --> 01:05:51,911
Really.

1104
01:05:52,000 --> 01:05:54,195
Uh, please tell me
you didn't pay.

1105
01:05:54,280 --> 01:05:56,111
I didn't.

1106
01:05:56,200 --> 01:05:58,475
Max took us.

1107
01:05:58,560 --> 01:06:01,279
-Well, that must have been
some performance.
-<i>It was.</i>

1108
01:06:01,360 --> 01:06:04,636
<i>It's never been my favourite piece</i>
